<Proj>:
	name: "proj"
	GridLayout:
		cols: 1
		Label:
			size_hint_y: 0.1
			padding_x: 10
			text: "My Coding Journey"
			font_size: self.width/15
			bold: True
			text_size: self.size
			halign: "center"
			valign: "middle"
		Label:
			padding_x: 27
			padding_y: 10
			text_size: self.size
			font_size: self.height/38
			valign: "top"
			text: "I came to know about programming in 11th std (CS group but my school focussed only on JEE preparation) and I learned PYTHON as my first programming language. At that time, i had a only little interest in programming becuase it was very new to me. I was able to do the basic problems given by my teacher and thats it.\n\nThen came the lockdown and online classes and I started to get away from my studies and school stuff. Then my school gave us a group project in Python but I had to do it single handedly because my group was busy in JEE preparation and I had no interest in JEE. I successfully completed the project on my own and that was the moment when I realised that 'PROGRAMMING IS THE RIGHT CHOICE FOR ME !!'. It was the first time in my life that i was good at something.\n\n After the project i was done with Python and came back to JEE preparation and i had zero interest in it. My JEE score went down, also some Heartbreaks happened... i wasn't able to do anything in my studies. So once again, I came back to Python but this time, more seriously. I consistently learned and practiced new concepts from youtube.\n\nMy boards score was somewhat good.. with that, I got B.Tech IT in CEG and here I am.. with you guys <3\n"
		Button:
			size_hint_y: 0.1
			text: "Back"
			on_press: app.root.current='Wel'